4. Added proper spacing in some attribute values
5. Standardized the format of prices and other text elements
6. Fixed an apparent typo in "Annokationibus" to "Annotationibus" 
7. Corrected "Lieium" to "Livium" (referring to the Roman historian Livy)
8. Fixed "Eremplar" to "Exemplar"
9. Corrected various other small typos and standardized the text"}
